Row.Cell: You're bleeding. Unless you bandage your wounds, you'll slowly lose health and die. The bleeding won't stop on its own.
Sa veritsed. Kui sa ei seo kinni enda haavu, jooksed sa verest tühjaks ning sured. Verejooks ei lõppe iseenesest.
You don't move around, so you don't get tired or hungry.
Sa ei liigu, nii et sa ei väsi ega nälgi.
You have a +2 permanent bonus on Charisma, but also a -2 Strength penalty.
Sul on +2 püsiv Karisma boonus, aga ka -2 Jõu trahv
Your reputation is strong enough for you to get a bonus on Strength, Speech, Agility and Vitality. But you face tougher penalties for wrongdoing and your reputation improves more slowly.
Sinu maine on piisavalt tugev, et saaksid Jõu, Kõne, Väleduse ja Elujõu boonuse, kuid sind ootavad suuremad trahvid pattude eest ning sinu maine paraneb aeglasemalt.
You have the luck of the drunk and pick locks twice as easily, but make 30% more noise doing it.
Sul on joodiku õnn ja muukimine õnnestub kaks korda kergemini, aga see teeb 30% võrra rohkem häält.
Your eloquence increases when you haggle.
Sinu kõnepruuk paraneb, kui sa kaupled.
You're wanted. You're conspicuousness is reduced and your crimes are more quickly forgotten.
Sa oled tagaotsiav. Sinu silmatorkavus on vähendatud ning sinu kuritöö unustatakse kiiremini.
You get a permanent +2 bonus on Vitality.
